select /*+ set_var(new_planner_optimize_timeout = 10000) */ 1 as relation_key ,
		sum(ads_sp_cost) as ads_sp_cost ,
		sum(shared_ads_sb_cost) as shared_ads_sb_cost ,
		sum(shared_ads_sbv_cost) as shared_ads_sbv_cost ,
		sum(ads_sd_cost) as ads_sd_cost ,
		sum(shared_cost_of_advertising) as shared_cost_of_advertising ,
		sum(spend) as spend ,
		sum(gross_profit) as gross_profit ,
		sum(df_amount) as df_amount
	from
		(
		select
			ads_sp_cost ,
			shared_ads_sb_cost ,
			shared_ads_sbv_cost ,
			ads_sd_cost ,
			shared_cost_of_advertising ,
			spend ,
			gross_profit ,
			df_amount ,
			unnest as principal_uids
		from
			(
			select
				coalesce(dpr.principal_uids, '-1') as principal_uids ,
				sum(coalesce(t.ads_sp_cost, 0) * m_cny_rate.rate / m_target_rate.rate) as ads_sp_cost ,
				sum(coalesce(t.shared_ads_sb_cost, 0) * m_cny_rate.rate / m_target_rate.rate) as shared_ads_sb_cost ,
				sum(coalesce(t.shared_ads_sbv_cost, 0) * m_cny_rate.rate / m_target_rate.rate) as shared_ads_sbv_cost ,
				sum(coalesce(t.ads_sd_cost, 0) * m_cny_rate.rate / m_target_rate.rate) as ads_sd_cost ,
				sum(coalesce(t.shared_cost_of_advertising, 0) * m_cny_rate.rate / m_target_rate.rate) as shared_cost_of_advertising ,
				0 as spend ,
				sum(( coalesce(t.total_sales_amount, 0) + coalesce(t.shipping_credits, 0) + coalesce(t.promotional_rebates, 0) + coalesce(t.fba_inventory_credit, 0) + coalesce(t.cash_on_delivery, 0) + coalesce(t.other_in_amount, 0) ) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) / coalesce(m_target_rate.rate, 1)) as df_amount ,
				sum((coalesce(t.total_sales_amount, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.shipping_credits, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.promotional_rebates, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.fba_inventory_credit, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.cash_on_delivery, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.other_in_amount, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.total_sales_refunds, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.total_fee_refunds, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.platform_fee, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.fba_delivery_fee, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.other_transaction_fees, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.total_spend, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.promotion_fee, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.total_storage_fee, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.shared_fba_integerernational_inbound_fee, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.total_platform_other_fee, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) + coalesce(t.adjustments, 0) * coalesce(m_cny_rate.rate, 1) - coalesce(dpr.cg_price * t.cg_price_quantity, 0) * coalesce(m_cg_price_cny_rate.rate, 1) - coalesce(dpr.cg_transport_costs * t.cg_transport_costs_quantity, 0) * coalesce(m_cg_transport_costs_cny_rate.rate, 1) ) / coalesce(m_target_rate.rate, 1)) as gross_profit
			from
				(
				select
					t.posted_date_locale as r_date ,
					dsr.zid ,
					dsr.sid ,
					t.seller_sku ,
					coalesce(shared_ads_sb_cost, 0) + coalesce(shared_ads_sbv_cost, 0) + coalesce(ads_sd_cost, 0) + coalesce(ads_sp_cost, 0) as total_spend ,
					null as shared_cost_of_advertising ,
					coalesce(ads_sd_cost, 0) + coalesce(ads_sp_cost, 0) as new_ad_total_spend ,
					coalesce(shared_ads_sb_cost, 0) as shared_ads_sb_cost ,
					coalesce(shared_ads_sbv_cost, 0) as shared_ads_sbv_cost ,
					coalesce(ads_sd_cost, 0) as ads_sd_cost ,
					coalesce(ads_sp_cost, 0) as ads_sp_cost ,
					( coalesce(other_fba_product_sales, 0) + coalesce(principal_fba_product_sales, 0) + coalesce(reship_fba_product_sales, 0) + coalesce(shared_other_fba_product_sales, 0) + coalesce(other_fbm_product_sales, 0) + coalesce(principal_fbm_product_sales, 0) + coalesce(reship_fbm_product_sales, 0) + coalesce(gift_wrap_credits, 0) + coalesce(a_to_z_guarantee_claims, 0) + coalesce(cost_of_points_granted, 0) ) as total_sales_amount ,
					coalesce(shipping_credits, 0) as shipping_credits ,
					(coalesce(promotional_rebates, 0) + + coalesce(shared_promotional_rebates, 0)) as promotional_rebates ,
					( coalesce(fba_inventory_credit, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_inventory_credit, 0) ) as fba_inventory_credit ,
					coalesce(shared_cash_on_delivery, 0) as cash_on_delivery ,
					( coalesce(shared_fba_liquidation_proceeds, 0) + coalesce(shared_amazon_shipping_reimbursement, 0) + coalesce(shared_safe_t_reimbursement, 0) + coalesce(shared_netco_transaction, 0) + coalesce(shared_reimbursements, 0) + coalesce(shared_clawbacks, 0) + coalesce(shared_others, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_liquidation_proceeds_adjustments, 0) + coalesce(shared_commingling_vat_income, 0) ) as other_in_amount ,
					( coalesce(other_fba_product_sale_refunds, 0) + coalesce(principal_fba_product_sale_refunds, 0) + coalesce(reship_fba_product_sale_refunds, 0) + coalesce(other_fbm_product_sale_refunds, 0) + coalesce(principal_fbm_product_sale_refunds, 0) + coalesce(reship_fbm_product_sale_refunds, 0) + coalesce(shipping_credit_refunds, 0) + coalesce(gift_wrap_credit_refunds, 0) + coalesce(chargebacks, 0) + coalesce(cost_of_points_returned, 0) + coalesce(promotional_rebate_refunds, 0) + coalesce(shared_promotional_rebate_refunds, 0) ) as total_sales_refunds ,
					( coalesce(selling_fee_refunds, 0) + coalesce(fba_transaction_fee_refunds, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_transaction_fee_refunds, 0) + coalesce(refund_administration_fees, 0) + coalesce(other_transaction_fee_refunds, 0) + coalesce(shared_refund_for_advertiser, 0) + coalesce(points_adjusted, 0) + coalesce(shipping_label_refunds, 0) + coalesce(shared_shipping_label_refunds, 0) ) as total_fee_refunds ,
					( coalesce(seller_fulfilled_selling_fees, 0) + coalesce(fba_selling_fees, 0) ) as platform_fee ,
					( coalesce(other_fba_transaction_fees, 0) + coalesce(mc_fba_fulfillment_fees, 0) + coalesce(shared_other_fba_transaction_fees, 0) ) as fba_delivery_fee ,
					(coalesce(other_transaction_fees, 0) + coalesce(shared_other_transaction_fees, 0)) as other_transaction_fees ,
					( coalesce(shared_subscription_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_ld_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_coupon_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_early_reviewer_program_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_vine_fee, 0) ) as promotion_fee ,
					( coalesce(fba_storage_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_storage_fee, 0) + coalesce(long_term_storage_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_long_term_storage_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_storage_renewal_billing, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_disposal_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_removal_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_inbound_transportation_program_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_labeling_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_polybagging_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_bubblewrap_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_taping_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_customer_return_fee, 0) + coalesce(fba_customer_return_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_inbound_defect_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_overage_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_amazon_partnered_carrier_shipment_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_fba_inbound_convenience_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_item_fee_adjustment, 0) + coalesce(shared_other_fba_inventory_fees, 0) ) as total_storage_fee ,
					coalesce(shared_fba_international_inbound_fee, 0) as shared_fba_integerernational_inbound_fee ,
					( coalesce(shipping_label_purchases, 0) + coalesce(shared_shipping_label_purchases, 0) + coalesce(shared_carrier_shipping_label_adjustments, 0) + coalesce(shared_liquidations_fees, 0) + coalesce(shared_manual_processing_fee, 0) + coalesce(shared_other_service_fees, 0) ) as total_platform_other_fee ,
					( coalesce(adjustments, 0) + coalesce(shared_adjustments, 0) ) as adjustments ,
					(coalesce(principal_fbm_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(principal_fba_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(reship_fbm_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(reship_fba_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(mc_fba_fulfillment_fees_quantity, 0) - coalesce(fba_returns_quantity, 0) ) AS cg_price_quantity ,
					(coalesce(principal_fbm_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(principal_fba_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(reship_fbm_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(reship_fba_product_sales_quantity, 0) + coalesce(mc_fba_fulfillment_fees_quantity, 0) - coalesce(fba_returns_quantity, 0) ) AS cg_transport_costs_quantity
				from
					(
					select
						a.* ,
						get_json_double(a.`__extend_fields`,
						'$.shared_other_transaction_fees') as shared_other_transaction_fees ,
						get_json_double(a.`__extend_fields`,
						'$.shared_shipping_label_refunds') as shared_shipping_label_refunds ,
						get_json_double(a.`__extend_fields`,
						'$.shared_promotional_rebates') as shared_promotional_rebates ,
						get_json_double(a.`__extend_fields`,
						'$.shared_promotional_rebate_refunds') as shared_promotional_rebate_refunds
					from
						(
						select
							* ,
							row_number() over(partition by company_id,
							seller_id,
							country_code,
							seller_sku,
							posted_date_locale
						order by
							id desc) rn
						from
							daily_profit_statis_v4 t
						where
							company_id = 901117781768839168
							and t.posted_date_locale >= '2022-08-01'
							and t.posted_date_locale <= '2022-08-31' ) a
					where
						rn = 1 ) t
				inner join dim_seller_rf dsr on
					t.seller_id = dsr.seller_id
					and t.country_code = dsr.code
					and t.company_id = dsr.company_id
				where
					dsr.zid = 1 ) t
			inner join (
				select
					t.zid ,
					t.sid ,
					t.asin ,
					t.seller_sku ,
					t.parent_asin ,
					t.local_sku ,
					t.cg_price ,
					if(length(t.cg_price_currency_code) > 0,
					t.cg_price_currency_code,
					'CNY') as cg_price_currency_code ,
					t.cg_transport_costs ,
					if(length(t.cg_transport_costs_currency_code) >0,
					t.cg_transport_costs_currency_code,
					'CNY') as cg_transport_costs_currency_code ,
					s.seller_id ,
					s.code as country_code ,
					s.currency_code ,
					s.currency_icon ,
					s.mid ,
					t.company_id ,
					t.principal_uids
				from
					dim_product_rf t
				inner join (
					select
						*
					from
						dim_seller_rf t
					where
						t.zid = 1 ) s on
					t.zid = s.zid
					and t.sid = s.sid
				where
					t.zid = 1
					and t.company_id = 901117781768839168
					and t.is_parent != 1
					) dpr on
				dpr.zid = t.zid
				and dpr.sid = t.sid
				and dpr.seller_sku = t.seller_sku
			left join (
				select
					zid,
					code,
					icon,
					rate,
					date
				from
					company_currency_month
				where
					zid = 1
					and date between substring( '2022-08-01' , 1, 7) and substring( '2022-08-31' , 1, 7) ) m_cny_rate on
				dpr.zid = m_cny_rate.zid
				and dpr.currency_code = m_cny_rate.code
				and substring(t.r_date, 1, 7)= m_cny_rate.date
			left join (
				select
					zid,
					code,
					icon,
					rate,
					date
				from
					company_currency_month
				where
					zid = 1
					and date between substring( '2022-08-01' , 1, 7) and substring( '2022-08-31' , 1, 7) ) m_cg_price_cny_rate on
				dpr.zid = m_cny_rate.zid
				and dpr.cg_price_currency_code = m_cny_rate.code
				and substring(t.r_date, 1, 7)= m_cny_rate.date
			left join (
				select
					zid ,
					code ,
					icon ,
					rate ,
					date
				from
					company_currency_month
				where
					zid = 1
					and date between substring( '2022-08-01' , 1, 7) and substring( '2022-08-31' , 1, 7) ) m_cg_transport_costs_cny_rate on
				dpr.zid = m_cg_transport_costs_cny_rate.zid
				and dpr.cg_transport_costs_currency_code = m_cg_transport_costs_cny_rate.code
				and substring(t.r_date, 1, 7) = m_cg_transport_costs_cny_rate.date
			left join (
				select
					zid,
					code,
					icon,
					rate,
					date
				from
					company_currency_month
				where
					zid = 1
					and date between substring( '2022-08-01' , 1, 7) and substring( '2022-08-31' , 1, 7)
						and code = 'USD' ) m_target_rate on
				dpr.zid = m_cny_rate.zid
				and substring(t.r_date, 1, 7)= m_target_rate.date
			group by
				dpr.principal_uids ) a ,
			unnest(split(principal_uids,
			',')) ) a;

table_meta.data_masking.company_currency_month:
CREATE TABLE `company_currency_month` (
  `id` bigint(20) NOT NULL COMMENT "",
  `zid` int(11) NOT NULL COMMENT "ID",
  `code` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "code",
  `icon` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "（：￥）",
  `name` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "（：）",
  `rate` decimal128(18, 10) NULL DEFAULT "0.0000" COMMENT "",
  `official_rate` decimal128(19, 6) NULL COMMENT "",
  `sort` int(11) NULL DEFAULT "99" COMMENT "99，1，",
  `update_uid` int(11) NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "UID",
  `is_update` int(11) NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "python",
  `date` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `gmt_modified` datetime NULL COMMENT "",
  `gmt_create` datetime NULL COMMENT "",
  `update_time` varchar(65533) NULL COMMENT "",
  `rate_long` decimal64(18, 10) NULL DEFAULT "0.0000000000" COMMENT "(10)",
  `official_rate_long` decimal64(18, 10) NULL DEFAULT "0.0000000000" COMMENT "(10)",
  `company_id` bigint(20) NULL DEFAULT "0" COMMENT "id",
  `v_uuid` varchar(120) NULL DEFAULT "" COMMENT "BGID，"
) ENGINE=OLAP 
PRIMARY KEY(`id`)
COMMENT "【】"
DISTRIBUTED BY HASH(`id`) BUCKETS 1 
PROPERTIES (
"replication_num" = "1",
"in_memory" = "false",
"storage_format" = "DEFAULT",
"enable_persistent_index" = "false",
"compression" = "LZ4"
);
